[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "ニオ",
		"romanized_name": "Nio",
		"model_path_hash": "1882786194477430238",
		"text": "あっ、見つけた！\nおねーちゃん！　探していた素材だよ！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8735269928136797011",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "アーシャ",
		"romanized_name": "Ayesha",
		"model_path_hash": "7148606200211237631",
		"text": "思ったより、たくさん咲いてるね。\nこれだけあれば、薬の調合には十分かな",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5225548852493309829",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "……ここまで群生してるのは、初めて見た",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "アーシャ",
		"romanized_name": "Ayesha",
		"model_path_hash": "7148606200211237631",
		"text": "わたしも。ここは土の質も良さそうだし、\n湿度も絶妙……やっぱり自然の力ってすごいなあ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5225548852493309829",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "……この景色、いいわね。風の匂いも、\n木々の揺れ方も。物語に書き残したくなる",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "アーシャ",
		"romanized_name": "Ayesha",
		"model_path_hash": "7148606200211237631",
		"text": "ユリエさん、旅の記録は順調ですか？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5225548852493309829",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "ええ。言葉じゃ伝えきれないかもしれないけれど……\nこういう素敵な景色を、私なりに文章にしているわ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "私、ここの土壌成分を調べてみたい。\n薬草の成分変化も気になるし",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "アーシャ",
		"romanized_name": "Ayesha",
		"model_path_hash": "7148606200211237631",
		"text": "あ、わたしも。この花、育った土によって\n香りが変わるんだって",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5225548852493309829",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ニオ",
		"romanized_name": "Nio",
		"model_path_hash": "1882786194477430238",
		"text": "……錬金術士ってやっぱりすごいなあ。\nわたしは土まで調べようってならないもん",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8735269928136797011",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "リンカ",
		"romanized_name": "Linca",
		"model_path_hash": "2320534114475787876",
		"text": "私には薬士の考えることも分かりません……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "4464667044946317190",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ニオ",
		"romanized_name": "Nio",
		"model_path_hash": "1882786194477430238",
		"text": "ふふ。でも、おねーちゃんたちが楽しそうで嬉しいな",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8735269928136797011",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "ニオ、あなたも旅を楽しんでるのね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ニオ",
		"romanized_name": "Nio",
		"model_path_hash": "1882786194477430238",
		"text": "はい！　おねーちゃんと、みんなと\n一緒に歩けるのが一番です",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8735269928136797011",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "…………",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "ニオ",
		"romanized_name": "Nio",
		"model_path_hash": "1882786194477430238",
		"text": "それにしても二人が一緒に旅してるの、珍しいよね。\nミルカちゃんも、お姉さんのお手伝いとか？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8735269928136797011",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "……私は素材採取のついで",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "ミルカはこんな感じだけど、\nいざという時は頼りになるのよ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "ニオ",
		"romanized_name": "Nio",
		"model_path_hash": "1882786194477430238",
		"text": "ふふ、そうなんですね！\nわたしも、おねーちゃんのために頑張るから！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8735269928136797011",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "アーシャ",
		"romanized_name": "Ayesha",
		"model_path_hash": "7148606200211237631",
		"text": "ニオ……無理しないでね？\nあまり一人で離れすぎたりもしちゃダメだよ？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5225548852493309829",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "ニオ",
		"romanized_name": "Nio",
		"model_path_hash": "1882786194477430238",
		"text": "もう、分かってるよ。大丈夫。\nわたしだって、おねーちゃんの役に立ちたいんだもん",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8735269928136797011",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "リンカ",
		"romanized_name": "Linca",
		"model_path_hash": "2320534114475787876",
		"text": "大丈夫です、アーシャ。\n私もいますから",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "4464667044946317190",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "アーシャ",
		"romanized_name": "Ayesha",
		"model_path_hash": "7148606200211237631",
		"text": "うん、ありがとう、リンカさん。\nニオも……ありがとう",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5225548852493309829",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "ニオ",
		"romanized_name": "Nio",
		"model_path_hash": "1882786194477430238",
		"text": "うん！　えへへ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8735269928136797011",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "姉妹って、いいものね。\n見ていると心が温かくなる",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "……そういうの、あまり言わないで。かゆいから",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "リンカ",
		"romanized_name": "Linca",
		"model_path_hash": "2320534114475787876",
		"text": "皆さん、そろそろ夜になりそうです。\n目的のものも見つかりましたし、森を抜けましょう",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "4464667044946317190",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "リンカ",
		"romanized_name": "Linca",
		"model_path_hash": "2320534114475787876",
		"text": "お二人は、この後どこへ向かわれるのですか？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "4464667044946317190",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "このまま東へ抜けて、クア州へ行くわ。\nその後は、時計回りで各州を見て行くつもりよ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "リンカ",
		"romanized_name": "Linca",
		"model_path_hash": "2320534114475787876",
		"text": "長い旅になりそうですね……\n旅の無事を願っています",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "4464667044946317190",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "ええ、ありがとう",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]